 color: #373c40; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p12 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p13 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333; min-height: 14.0px} p.p14 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Hiragino Sans GB'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p15 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Hiragino Sans GB'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333; min-height: 24.0px} span.s1 {font: 15.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 14.0px Arial; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 15.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; font-kerning: none; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #323333} span.s5 {font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-kerning: none; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #393939} span.s6 {font: 24.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #373c40; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #373c40} span.s7 {font: 15.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #999999; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #999999} span.s8 {font: 16.0px 'Hiragino Sans GB'; font-kerning: none} span.s9 {font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/25068.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>上汽“辉昂 PHIDEON” 找乔治·克鲁尼做代言人，并拍摄了一支 TVC。</b></a>“辉昂 PHIDEON” 是 2016 年上市的上汽大众旗下首款 C 级豪华轿车，产品定位瞄准中高端消费者。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=j0339zt7pkl&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/01/05/xuweizhou-the-face-of-coach-men-china/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>许魏洲成为 Coach 首位男士产品全系列中国区代言人</b></a>，并公布平面广告大片。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108115302rI2kuaTqVRxCFch1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.357407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/01/05/find-my-tokyo-kicks-out-a-new-campaign-with-satomi-180105/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>石原里美为东京 Metro 拍摄了《Find my Tokyo》的第四支宣传片。</b></a>新的广告片中，十元与客串的日本歌姬绚香乘坐着东京 Metro 运营的千代田线到了西日暮里，开始了两个姐妹花自拍互拍的一天。东京 Metro 希望通过石原里美的个人视角来宣传东京的魅力，吸引更多游客。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=y0529aaxhqc&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5OTU5MzIxNA==&amp;mid=2651346747&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=54e69d0ee7ebe71e9fbae604f51376e1&amp;chksm=bcc5e2aa8bb26bbcdf4fc0d1eb601f7c7012fb0b1a49737d64a38f4b9d66fd2a786a969e983a&amp;scene=0&amp;key=44b46647b1773bae3b25197d1b8169d0813c8d37cc14df21dcea65f638e0c8e5996da32e8a0b21c35a2b66849302ad609f4abd1b663bab824dc9cc40fb30a8b2ad9ba7b2431e15d02360408519f62c22&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MTIyNTYzODY0MA%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir6%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.10.5+build(14F2511)&amp;version=11000006&amp;lang=zh_CN&amp;pass_ticket=nBD5WQS1KcywdHk82ixhKQUJw1v0TXhltvuVFekwwKDin4oBLZkWDte3UzP1gL9A\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Bilibili 弹幕网和罗森合作开主题店</b></a>，主题店共分为上下二层，一楼为购物区，二楼为休憩区。上架了各种以小电视、22 娘、33 娘为主要形象设计的各式周边，开业打八折。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108120737XPZEC4dVlj0xyaMe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108164538wARzHeq2Ed1vQ7mx.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667052\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108164450nFZMHtibOpgPVsko.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667052\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108164508trS69RbKYdvkZhoE.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665509\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p><b><a href=\"http://www.sportsmoney.cn/article/74134.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">肯德基与吃鸡游戏合作</a>，</b>在 1 月 7 日至 1 月 21 日期间玩 CF 荒岛特训，有机会得到半价优惠券，CF 炸鸡桶内包含 10 块香辣鸡翅、3 块吮指原味鸡和 3 杯大可乐。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801081155250dsB1AHEJONjMCQe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562977\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4193146956440811?wm=3333_2001&amp;from=1079293010&amp;sourcetype=weixin&amp;featurecode=newtitle\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>汉堡王和饿了么合作二次元营销</b></a>，在<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/n/%E9%A5%BF%E4%BA%86%E4%B9%88%E7%BD%91%E4%B8%8A%E8%AE%A2%E9%A4%90\" rel=\"nofollow\">@饿了么网上订餐</a> 全国独家发售7 折起“叶修福利堡”套餐，上海、杭州还有两家叶修主题店，还赠送 30 套叶神福利卡一波流送出。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108120056F50qWIdmXDBSYl3h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.560109\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的案例</h3><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/25074.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">天猫为冬季狂欢节发布一支 TVC</a></b>，这是天猫首次在冬季打造狂欢节，也是阿里巴巴在作为 2018 年至 2028 年奥运会的顶级合作伙伴后的首次亮相。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=y0526yrvbko&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/25087.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>中国气象局推出宣传片《神秘的黑衣人》和《有你陪伴的日子》</b></a>，温情又搞怪。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801081204001GeOMjgWyDE0iZL6.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.374710\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180108120559TBrF5jgHbi8qNDOh.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.477306\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p><b><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/43117\" rel=\"nofollow\">午后红茶做了个实验广告“恋爱体温实验”</a>，</b>拍摄了一堆异地恋的情侣，实时记录他们在聊到对方时候、见面时的体温变化。这是午后红茶以“温度感”为主题做的冬季营销。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=i0529sabzhv&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\">题图来源：罗森微信</p><style>\r\n\r\n</style>"}